beer.beer_description:
There’s something uniquely appealing about the idea of a refreshing, sessionable ale tailor-made for the South Pacific Summer. On the other hand there is nothing appealing at all about a flavourless beer. With the intention of organising the former without risking the latter, Tuatara has created Outrigger.

Beautifully pale in the pour, it’s loaded with suitably tropical hints of passionfruit, pineapple and mango from the latest Australian Galaxy hops.

The perfect summer brew for the perfect summer day. Beach your canoe somewhere shady and enjoy.
